This refers to an alert aboard a ship, usually a naval warship, summoning the crew to man all weapons and all stations. 

It is also known in the [[United States Navy|US Navy]] as "General Quarters," and in the UK Navy as "Action Stations." In the TV Series Star trek, it was referred to as "Red Alert."

See also [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:The_Epopt/Sub_alarms sub alarms] entry for discusion of various alerts and alarms on US NAvy submarines. 

